title: Sleep Better Instantly Using These Uncommon And Controversial Methods With Tim James
itunes:title: Sleep Better Instantly Using These Uncommon And Controversial Methods With Tim James
description:
If you missed it, Tim James was just on episode 325, but Zach was so impressed with him that he’s back again.  Tim is a true master of his craft and the best health expert this podcast has ever seen.  Zach, personally, has seen the quality of his life improve by following Tim’s recommendations.  The most recent product recommendation Tim has made was for grounding pads.  Zach says the first night he used it, he slept like a baby.

Tim is full of all the information you wish you didn’t know. From toxins in supplements to performance wear.  Someone, somewhere is profiting off of your poor health. The only way to combat this is through independent education. Knowledge is everywhere and it’s up to us to seek it out. Take back your health, don’t blindly follow the masses.  Trust nature, it’s where you come from and how we evolve. 

Show Notes: https://underdogempowerment.com/sleep-better-instantly
